Summary::md.summary
  Windows' version of gdndc is implemented with Qt, one version in
  Python and one version in C++. Qt is a fat as fuck dependency and
  using Python subjects you to the pain of packaging python. It should
  be possible to use native windows controls and webview2 or whatever
  for the rendering. Win32 is misery though, so meh.
